      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHEEZEL (5) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 20.13 beating KEIKI POLU. Looks to have an edge on most of these. BIG BUCKETS (4) fast out of the inside draw with a slick early sectional and clocking 23.43 in a one length win at Casino over 411m last time. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. CASH IN COLOUR (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.28) at this track behind Nitro Slim in a Mix 2/3. Has the pace to be prominent. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Can feature again. KEIKI POLU (8) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage second (20.20) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw.",
